descriptions: You can download a trial version of this app to try it for 15 minutes for free.
You won’t be charged anything when this free trial ends. You can’t make in-app purchases or use add-on content during this free trial, but you’ll keep any achievements you earn.

display_long_description:
Step into Cat Cafe, a highly immersive VR experience filled with adorable feline companions and endless possibilities. 

 😹 **Cat Memes Come Alive**

From the Spinning OI Cat to the Crying Cat, your favorite cat memes are hidden all around—see how many you can spot!
[media]

🐱 **Feel the Fur**

In Cat Cafe, every gentle stroke triggers lifelike feedback—you’ll sense the soft give of tiny muscles and joints, as if the cats were really right beside you.
[media]

💕 **Care and Cuddles**

From preparing yummy kibble to washing a muddy kitten clean, every act of care deepens their affection—and your furry friends will remember your kindness!
[media]

🧶 **Playtime Fun**

Wave a cat teaser, chase a mysterious laser dot—each toy sparks your cat’s playful hunting instincts and fills your moments together with giggles and soft purrs.
[media]

🕵️ **Discover the Unexpected**

And there’s so much more to discover! Come find out what fun awaits!
